{"tid":926577,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[swift/xcode撚入]新手求指導delegate問題","createTime":"2018-12-03T14:15:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-12T12:31:10.000Z","uid":14054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"17a76aaccb2f9b522f54b4164734e70373792592","tid":926577,"uid":14054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T14:15:46.000Z","msg":"初學Swift, 跟過網上啲教學寫過幾個簡單app<br />\n跟住黎做都叫睇得明，但去到關於用delegate 就睇到頭都大埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以講下delegate同protocol 係應該幾時用同點用?<br />\n<br />\n或者可以講下你當初係點樣明白呢個concept<br />\n<br />\n利申：冇乜programming底，叫做睇得明for loop while loop嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b8d260f343f32978dde19e4c688f472084da697","tid":926577,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T15:59:52.000Z","msg":"Delegate既慨念 係系統有event/總之有野要做  委派比你提供既野去做野<br />\n<br />\n至於點解有咁多design pattern 例如delegate呀protocol呀event呀signal呀 唔嚴謹咁講 其實全部都係類似既野 只係唔同人發明出黎 有唔同風格"},{"pid":"f46429d1287add0fbfd532c35daa9f7e786bb227","tid":926577,"uid":23953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-03T17:17:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Composition_over_inheritance?wprov=sfla1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.m.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FComposition_over_inheritance%3Fwprov%3Dsfla1&d=R1krSDJj3ONsglQoqLUBJcP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=03174229\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Composition_over_inheritance?wprov=sfla1</a><br />\ndesign patterns 有個最大原則，係 don't repeat yourself<br />\nprotocol 同 delegate 係其中一種 OOP code reuse pattern, 都係屬於composition, 另一個極端係 inheritance"},{"pid":"04087e723a0e34b0ce6f1d16cf7c07c64f0198e6","tid":926577,"uid":125569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T12:31:10.000Z","msg":"最普遍係 view controller 之間溝通用"}]}